# Security Review

Date: 2026-07-04
Department: Information Security
Attendees: Daniel Chen, Priya Sharma

## Issues Addressed

- Two laptops were reported missing from the contractor onboarding inventory.
- Device management shows one laptop has not checked in for seven days.
- Security wants ownership confirmed before opening an incident.

## Decisions

- Asset management will verify device assignment records.
- If ownership is unknown by end of day, Security will open an incident ticket.

## Action Items

- Fetch the assigned owner for the missing laptop asset IDs.
- Prepare a Jira incident if the asset owner cannot be confirmed.

